These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-1::.
Flower: dahlia, poppy, iris, lily
Sport: cycling, ice-hockey, soccer, weightlifting
1. Flower:dahlia is on the right of Sport:soccer##1
2. Sport:weightlifting is on the far left##1
3. Sport:soccer is between Sport:ice-hockey and Flower:poppy##2
4. Flower:lily is on the far left##1
5. Flower:iris is between Flower:poppy and Flower:dahlia##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |    3     |     4      |
| Flower   | lily         | poppy   | iris | dahlia       |
| Sport      | weightlifting | cycling | soccer   | ice-hockey |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-2::.
Hobby: gardening, magic-tricks, reading, video-games
Music-Genre: folk, hip-hop, r&b, d&b
1. Music-Genre:d&b is between Hobby:reading and Music-Genre:hip-hop##2
2. Hobby:video-games is on the far right##1
3. Music-Genre:r&b is on the right of Music-Genre:folk##1
4. Hobby:gardening is on the left of Music-Genre:folk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |    3    |      4      |
| Hobby         | magic-tricks | gardening | reading | video-games |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop    | d&b   | folk | r&b       |

