.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-3::.
Food: cauliflower, corn, cranberry, kale
Job: journalist, videographer, lawyer, manager
1. Job:lawyer is on the right of Food:kale##1
2. Job:lawyer is between Job:videographer and Food:corn##2
3. Job:videographer is on the far left##1
4. Job:manager is on the left of Food:cranberry##1
5. Food:corn == Job:manager##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |   3    |     4      |
| Food          | kale    | cauliflower | corn   | cranberry  |
| Job   | videographer | lawyer   | manager | journalist |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-4::.
Pet: cat, lizard, pony, rat
Color: blue, orange, white, fuchsia
1. Color:orange == Pet:lizard##1
2. Pet:cat is between Color:blue and Pet:rat##2
3. Color:orange is on the far right##1
4. Pet:cat is on the right of Color:white##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1   |   2    |     3      |    4     |
| Pet     | rat   | cat    | pony       | lizard   |
| Color   | white | fuchsia | blue | orange |

